### Phase C — Component Restyling (Layer 2-3, 3-5 commits)

**Цель:** Обновить styling всех компонентов чтобы соответствовали design reference.

#### C.1 — Button Component

```typescript
// BEFORE (Paper & Ink):
const VARIANT_CLASS: Record<PiButtonVariant, string> = {
  default: 'bg-sunrise-warm text-paper hover:opacity-90',
  secondary: 'bg-paper-2 text-ink hover:bg-paper',
  outline: 'bg-transparent hairline text-ink hover:bg-paper-2',
  ghost: 'bg-transparent text-ink hover:bg-paper-2',
  link: 'bg-transparent text-ink underline underline-offset-4 hover:text-ink',
  destructive: 'bg-destructive text-paper hover:opacity-90',
};

// AFTER (Design Reference):
const VARIANT_CLASS: Record<PiButtonVariant, string> = {
  default: 'bg-ink text-gold border border-gold executive-shadow hover:brightness-110',
  secondary: 'bg-tertiary text-white hover:brightness-110',
  outline: 'bg-transparent border border-rule text-ink hover:bg-paper-2',
  ghost: 'bg-transparent text-ink hover:bg-paper-2',
  link: 'bg-transparent text-ink underline underline-offset-4 hover:text-ink',
  destructive: 'bg-error text-white hover:brightness-110',
};
```

**Acceptance:**
- Primary button: charcoal bg + gold text + gold border + subtle shadow.
- Hover: brightness increases (not opacity).
- All buttons use JetBrains Mono uppercase (via `font-mono uppercase tracking-wider`).

#### C.2 — Badge Component

```typescript
// BEFORE (Paper & Ink):
const VARIANT_CLASS: Record<PiBadgeVariant, string> = {
  default: 'bg-transparent hairline border-sunrise-warm text-sunrise-warm',
  secondary: 'bg-transparent hairline border-rule text-ink',
  outline: 'bg-transparent hairline border-rule text-muted-foreground',
  destructive: 'bg-transparent hairline border-destructive text-destructive',
};

// AFTER (Design Reference):
const VARIANT_CLASS: Record<PiBadgeVariant, string> = {
  default: 'bg-gold/10 border border-gold/20 text-gold',
  secondary: 'bg-green-500/10 border border-green-500/20 text-green-700',
  outline: 'bg-surface-container border border-rule text-muted-foreground',
  destructive: 'bg-error/10 border border-error/20 text-error',
};
```

**Acceptance:**
- All badges use semi-transparent bg + border tint pattern.
- JetBrains Mono uppercase, 10-11px.
- No solid fills, no hairline-only approach.

#### C.3 — Card Component

```typescript
// ADD: executive-shadow to card shell
template: `
  <div class="hairline bg-paper rounded-lg executive-shadow p-6">
    <ng-content />
  </div>
`
```

**Acceptance:**
- Cards have subtle shadow (executive-shadow).
- Rounded-lg (0.25rem) per design ref.

