// UPDATE: focus ring to gold accent
// BEFORE: border-color: var(--color-ink);
// AFTER: border-color: var(--color-gold);
```

**Acceptance:**
- Inputs use 2px border-radius (design ref default).
- Focus ring shows gold accent border.

#### C.5 — Empty State Component

```typescript
// UPDATE: 2px dashed (via pi-dashed-panel utility change in Phase B)
// ADD: icon slot (Material Symbols or Lucide equivalent)
// ADD: action button slot
```

**Acceptance:**
