## 5. Risks and Tradeoffs

| Риск | Вероятность | Митигация |
|------|------------|-----------|
| Font change breaks existing layout (Hanken Grotesk is wider than Syne) | Средняя | Test all pages after font migration. Adjust spacing if needed. |
| Gold primary color clashes with existing sunrise-warm references | Средняя | Search-and-replace all sunrise-warm references to gold equivalents. |
| Executive-shadow conflicts with global `box-shadow: none !important` | Высокая | Remove the global shadow ban, apply `executive-shadow` explicitly to cards/panels only. |
| Badge semi-transparent pattern reduces readability on dark backgrounds | Низкая | Test on both light and dark surfaces. Adjust opacity if needed. |
| 2px border-radius too subtle for some components | Низкая | Design ref uses this intentionally. Keep as-is per design source. |
| Lucide icons don't match Material Symbols glyph names | Средняя | Document icon name mapping. Don't rename icons in this TZ — separate effort. |

